WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.669
Good morning family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.679 --> 00:00:05.309
be with you again today. I have some

00:00:05.319 --> 00:00:08.589
things I want to say. I was

00:00:08.599 --> 00:00:11.030
driving around this evening and

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.030
praying like I normally do, and the

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:15.709
Lord spoke to me. He said, 'Brandon, I

00:00:15.719 --> 00:00:18.349
want you to make a video entitled What

00:00:18.359 --> 00:00:21.070
Are You Believing For in

00:00:21.070 --> 00:00:21.080
2024?'and

00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:24.310
I want you to talk to the

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:28.109
people to encourage them to

00:00:28.119 --> 00:00:30.509
believe me for the

00:00:30.519 --> 00:00:32.069
impossible in

00:00:32.079 --> 00:00:35.310
2024. Believe for the impossible; believe

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:37.549
for something so big and so out

00:00:37.559 --> 00:00:40.150
of your comprehension that it would only

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:42.750
take God to move in your circumstances.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:44.190
That's what I'm talking

00:00:44.190 --> 00:00:44.200
about—something

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:45.069
so

00:00:45.079 --> 00:00:47.189
huge, not something

00:00:47.189 --> 00:00:47.199
easily

00:00:47.199 --> 00:00:49.069
achievable. You can believe for that, but

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:52.549
believe for something that without God's

00:00:52.559 --> 00:00:55.549
intervention, without God's help, it would

00:00:55.559 --> 00:00:57.590
be impossible to achieve.

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.310
That's what I'm trying to

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.110
say. Every

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:04.549
year, my wife and I write down everything

00:01:04.559 --> 00:01:06.190
we're believing for at the beginning of

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.910
the year. In January, we make the vision

00:01:08.910 --> 00:01:08.920
plain—the

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:10.550
Bible says, 'Write the vision

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:12.710
out and make it

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.710
plain.'We

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:16.270
write down everything we're believing

00:01:16.270 --> 00:01:16.280
for. For example,

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:17.870
right now we're believing for a new

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:19.749
home, a bigger house

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:22.630
for our family. We're believing for Megan.

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:25.390
It doesn't

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:28.069
matter; nothing's too big and nothing's

00:01:28.079 --> 00:01:31.590
too small. Put some small things on there

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.469
too, but I'm trying to encourage you that

00:01:34.479 --> 00:01:36.590
the Lord told me to come on here and

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:38.749
talk to you all about what you are

00:01:38.759 --> 00:01:42.109
believing for in 2024. Back in

00:01:42.119 --> 00:01:45.550
October, a man approached me and asked

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:49.069
me to pray with him for a spouse.

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:53.469
I told him, 'Write down every

00:01:53.479 --> 00:01:56.469
quality of what you're believing

00:01:56.469 --> 00:01:56.479
for.'Be

00:01:56.479 --> 00:01:58.270
realistic now; you don't have to be

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:00.670
flaky with it, like 'I want a blonde

00:02:00.670 --> 00:02:00.680
bombshell'or

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:02.870
whatever your heart's

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.990
desire is. God

00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:05.000
will

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.670
give you the desire of your

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:09.150
heart, but write down what you're

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:13.110
believing for in a Christian spouse.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.470
Petition the Lord for your new

00:02:22.480 --> 00:02:25.670
spouse. Believe God and petition him for

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:29.470
a child or whatever. Nothing's too big.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:31.910
You may be barren and unable to

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:34.750
have a child. Write the vision down:

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:38.030
'Lord, I'm believing you and I am

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:40.470
petitioning you, Father, for a baby for

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:43.550
our home.'But first, you

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:46.110
need to be married. Don't be trying to

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:48.309
believe God for a baby outside of

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:50.550
wedlock; you need to get

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.509
married first and make it

00:02:52.519 --> 00:02:55.030
right. Believe God for a

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:57.910
baby and he'll bring it to

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:00.270
pass. If he would bring a

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:02.550
baby in the deadness of Sarah's womb

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:05.710
with Abraham at 90-something years old, look

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:08.270
at what you could have. God's no

00:03:08.270 --> 00:03:08.280
respecter

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:09.990
of persons;

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.270
if he'll bless Abraham with a

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:15.630
baby, Isaac, he'll bless you

00:03:15.630 --> 00:03:15.640
too.

00:03:15.640 --> 00:03:18.110
I believe with all my heart.

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:20.430
You just lay hands on your stomach

00:03:20.440 --> 00:03:22.670
and start praying over your womb.

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:24.869
Start calling that in and saying,

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:27.589
'I call my ovaries to produce. I call my

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:30.110
uterus to do what it's called to do. I

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.509
call my husband's seed to produce in the

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:34.949
name of Jesus.'Lay hands on each other

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:37.670
and believe God for the supernatural in

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.670
your life. I've seen it happen, and

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.190
people come back and say, 'We're having a

00:03:41.190 --> 00:03:41.200
baby.'I'm

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:44.270
telling you, nothing's too

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:46.309
big for our God.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:56.429
If you ladies

00:03:56.439 --> 00:04:00.110
are believing for a husband, write

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:02.589
it down, pray over it, and take communion over

00:04:02.599 --> 00:04:05.149
it. Call that husband in. Put yourself in

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:07.229
a position to meet this

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:09.670
person. Like I told him, you may

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:12.270
need to relocate to a

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.990
different city. The Lord says, 'Hey,

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:17.229
your husband or your wife is

00:04:17.239 --> 00:04:19.909
in such-and-such place,'and you're

00:04:19.919 --> 00:04:21.830
believing for it, but you live in

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:23.710
Kalamazoo and they live somewhere

00:04:23.710 --> 00:04:23.720
else.

00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:26.030
Put

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:28.830
yourself in the position to hear him so

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:30.550
you will be in the right place at the

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.830
right time. The steps of the

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:35.189
righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:37.749
Remember that and believe him that

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.110
you'll be in the right place at the

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.670
right time. Be on the

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:45.110
lookout. Expectation brings the

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:46.990
manifestation of what you've been

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:49.110
believing for. He tells me that all the

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.390
time: 'Brandon, expectation brings your

00:04:51.390 --> 00:04:51.400
manifestation.'Be

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:54.629
expecting him to

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:55.670
bring the

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:58.029
manifestation. He's already paid the

00:04:58.039 --> 00:05:00.469
price for your healing, for your

00:05:00.479 --> 00:05:02.749
deliverance, for prosperity,

00:05:02.749 --> 00:05:02.759
or

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:05.830
whatever. But he said that he gives you

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:08.590
power to get it done. He gives you power

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.510
to get wealth.

00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:13.390
We have authority in this earth

00:05:15.080 --> 00:05:18.510
over basically

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:20.469
everything because we're seated

00:05:20.479 --> 00:05:21.749
with him in the heavenlies. According

00:05:21.749 --> 00:05:21.759
to Ephesians,

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:23.749
we are seated

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:26.390
with him in the

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:29.150
heavenlies, far above all principalities

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.629
and powers and

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:33.629
might. If we're seated with him and we

00:05:33.639 --> 00:05:36.110
are joint-heirs with him, nothing's too

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:37.350
big. That's what I'm trying to tell you

00:05:37.350 --> 00:05:37.360
all:

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:41.189
spouses, babies, finances,

00:05:41.199 --> 00:05:44.029
houses, whatever. But make the vision

00:05:44.039 --> 00:05:47.710
plain. Find scripture to stand on.

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.990
I'm going to say that again: find

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:53.629
scripture concerning your circumstances

00:05:53.639 --> 00:05:56.350
to believe God for. You have to have

00:05:56.360 --> 00:05:59.070
scripture to back your prayers. Don't

00:05:59.080 --> 00:06:02.189
just be praying flipping things,

00:06:02.199 --> 00:06:04.590
because you need word to back it. You

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:06.589
have to find word to back what you're

00:06:06.599 --> 00:06:09.230
believing for so that you know

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:11.390
it lines up with the word of God. He

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:13.070
doesn't want anybody to

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:17.950
be alone or barren. He said,

00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:19.629
'The fruit of your womb will be

00:06:19.629 --> 00:06:19.639
blessed.'My

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:22.270
vine will not cast its fruit

00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:24.550
before the time. If you have problems

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:24.560
with

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:27.390
miscarriages, my vine will not

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:29.870
cast fruit before the time, and he said

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:33.110
he rebukes the devourer for your sake. The

00:06:33.110 --> 00:06:33.120
devourer

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:35.629
is eating your seed, your

00:06:35.639 --> 00:06:38.230
fruit of your womb,

00:06:38.230 --> 00:06:38.240
and

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:41.710
you have authority over

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:43.790
that by praying and

00:06:43.800 --> 00:06:46.629
commissioning your womb not

00:06:46.629 --> 00:06:46.639
to

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:48.230
cast fruit before its time. That's in

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:52.110
Deuteronomy 28. Believe that and stand on the

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:53.629
word. I'm just

00:06:53.639 --> 00:06:55.189
trying to throw some things out there

00:06:55.189 --> 00:06:55.199
of

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:57.629
what you could believe for

00:06:57.629 --> 00:06:57.639
in

00:06:57.639 --> 00:07:00.350
2024. I felt a lot of

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:01.950
people are believing for children,

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:04.350
spouses,

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:06.510
or

00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:08.270
finances because they're

00:07:08.280 --> 00:07:10.110
broke and don't have enough to

00:07:10.120 --> 00:07:12.589
make it paycheck to paycheck. God is not

00:07:12.599 --> 00:07:15.430
a paycheck-to-paycheck God; he is an

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:18.230
overflow God that is exceedingly

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:20.550
abundantly above all that you dare ask

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:23.110
or think according to the power that

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:27.070
worketh in you. He is an overflow

00:07:27.080 --> 00:07:30.430
God. You may not own a home;

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:33.350
you may live in a rental house or a

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:35.110
lease,

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:38.790
and you want your own home. I

00:07:38.790 --> 00:07:38.800
drive

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:41.189
around and I dream all the

00:07:41.199 --> 00:07:42.990
time. I drive around and look at homes

00:07:42.990 --> 00:07:43.000
and

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:45.430
say, 'Father, I know that you're the God

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.990
that owns the cattle on a thousand hills,

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.550
and I know that

00:07:50.550 --> 00:07:50.560
you

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:53.070
produce wealth in my hands. Father,

00:07:53.080 --> 00:07:55.029
you'll take care of my family

00:07:55.029 --> 00:07:55.039
and

00:07:55.039 --> 00:07:57.749
we'll have a good house, a

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:00.070
place to lay our head at night that's

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:01.990
good and insulated, protects us in the

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.029
winter, and is good in the summer. Lord,

00:08:04.039 --> 00:08:05.550
I need a bigger

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:07.149
home so my daughter can have her own

00:08:07.159 --> 00:08:09.830
room, because my oldest one needs her own

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:11.790
room because she has special

00:08:11.790 --> 00:08:11.800
needs.'I

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:14.029
thank you, Lord, that not only you're

00:08:14.039 --> 00:08:16.189
going to heal Megan, but God, you'll

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:18.589
provide a bedroom for my

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:21.430
little one. That's what I do; I

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:23.749
pray for it and God gives you the desires

00:08:23.749 --> 00:08:23.759
of

00:08:23.759 --> 00:08:25.189
your heart. Ladies and gentlemen, I

00:08:25.199 --> 00:08:28.390
believe with all my heart he's not

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:31.029
broke. He's not up there going, 'Well, I got

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:33.110
to talk to Jesus and see if our bank

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:35.949
accounts are okay to provide

00:08:35.959 --> 00:08:38.550
a new home.'He

00:08:38.550 --> 00:08:38.560
doesn't go,

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:40.350
'Well, no, we're a little low up here

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:42.149
in heaven; we got to cash in one of our

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:44.470
gold bricks or

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.829
some pearls

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.949
because we're a little

00:08:49.949 --> 00:08:49.959
low.'No,

00:08:49.959 --> 00:08:54.310
he's an overflow God. He

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:56.750
has more than enough for you.

00:08:56.760 --> 00:08:58.110
He'll give

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:01.590
you a creative idea to get wealth. All

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:03.630
you have to do is switch over your

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:06.030
stinking thinking. It's your thinking;

00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:06.040
if

00:09:06.040 --> 00:09:08.750
it's

00:09:08.750 --> 00:09:08.760
poverty-minded,

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:11.150
you think, 'Well, God doesn't love me,

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.870
he's not going to take care of

00:09:12.870 --> 00:09:12.880
me.'No,

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:16.590
he loves you. Faith works by love.

00:09:21.959 --> 00:09:26.310
The Lord said, 'Brandon, there's

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.710
people on your channel that are asking

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:29.710
me

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:32.870
why their faith is not

00:09:32.880 --> 00:09:34.710
working.'He

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:39.030
said, 'Faith works by

00:09:39.030 --> 00:09:39.040
love.'If

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:41.670
you want to know why your

00:09:41.680 --> 00:09:44.190
prayers aren't getting answered when

00:09:44.190 --> 00:09:44.200
you're

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:46.230
petitioning him

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:49.790
for things like healing,

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:52.030
check

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:55.430
your love walk. If your love walk isn't

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:56.829
right with him and you're treating

00:09:56.839 --> 00:09:58.110
people like

00:09:58.110 --> 00:09:58.120
trash—your

00:09:58.120 --> 00:10:01.350
spouse, your kids,

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:04.110
your

00:10:05.949 --> 00:10:05.959
neighbor—love...

00:10:07.959 --> 00:10:13.069
faith works by love.

00:10:13.069 --> 00:10:13.079
It's

00:10:13.079 --> 00:10:14.230
that

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:17.670
simple. I automatically go

00:10:17.680 --> 00:10:21.030
to my love gauge, and if it isn't full

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:23.910
and you aren't walking in love, maybe

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:26.910
that's why your faith isn't working.

00:10:28.760 --> 00:10:31.230
It's so true and

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:34.350
real. The Bible even talks about

00:10:34.350 --> 00:10:34.360
how

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:36.230
if you aren't honoring your wife and

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.350
treating her with respect,

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:40.990
the Lord doesn't hear your prayers.

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:43.069
I don't have the exact street

00:10:43.079 --> 00:10:45.590
address for that

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.269
chapter and verse, but

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:50.310
it's in the Bible. Google

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:52.949
it. I'll have my son

00:10:52.959 --> 00:10:54.310
find it and put it in the

00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:56.269
video right here.

00:10:56.279 --> 00:10:58.230
If you don't

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:03.389
honor your wife and treat her right, your

00:11:03.399 --> 00:11:05.190
prayers aren't going to be heard.

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:07.430
You've got to honor your

00:11:07.430 --> 00:11:07.440
wives,

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.269
husbands; you've

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:11.069
got to treat them with respect and

00:11:11.079 --> 00:11:13.269
pray for them.

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:15.389
If you

00:11:15.399 --> 00:11:17.310
want your prayers to be answered, you've got

00:11:17.320 --> 00:11:19.509
to

00:11:19.509 --> 00:11:19.519
walk

00:11:19.519 --> 00:11:23.310
in love

00:11:23.310 --> 00:11:23.320
and

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:25.990
goodness. People do

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.030
you wrong all the time. I have a problem

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.550
sometimes holding a grudge,

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:31.910
and the Lord tells me, 'Love

00:11:31.920 --> 00:11:33.550
takes no account of a suffered wrong,

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:36.990
Brandon. You got to let it go.'Love takes

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.590
no account of a suffered wrong; love is

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:41.310
patient, love is kind. Look at all the

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:44.150
things the

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:45.990
Bible says love is.

00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:50.670
That's where you have to base where your

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:52.230
faith is at; it's like a

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:54.629
gauge. First

